<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 09:17:22 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>菲律宾称在与中国达成补给协议后仍维护南海权利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-still-assert-south-china-sea-rights-after-resupply-deal-with-2024-07-22/</link><description>菲律宾外交部周一表示，在与中国就向有争议的仁爱礁执行补给任务达成“临时安排”后，菲律宾将继续维护其在南海的权利。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 07:52:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-still-assert-south-china-sea-rights-after-resupply-deal-with-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国允许延迟退休以应对人口问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-allow-delayed-retirement-combat-population-woes-2024-07-22/</link><description>中国将逐步提高法定退休年龄（目前是世界上最低的退休年龄之一），以允许人们工作更长时间，因为中国正在努力缓解养老金预算不断飙升的压力，许多省份已经面临赤字。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 07:51:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-allow-delayed-retirement-combat-population-woes-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国对其十年来的政策承诺的承诺面临越来越多的质疑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-faces-growing-scepticism-over-its-commitment-decade-old-policy-pledges-2024-07-22/</link><description>随着中国经济失衡加剧，北京方面面临的压力越来越大，要求兑现其在上周领导层议程制定会议上重申的长达十年之久的政策承诺，但近年来未能取得重大突破。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 07:06:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-faces-growing-scepticism-over-its-commitment-decade-old-policy-pledges-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>西方矿商推动金属价格上涨以抵御中国竞争对手</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/western-miners-push-higher-metals-prices-ward-off-chinese-rivals-2024-07-22/</link><description>美国唯一的钴矿位于爱达荷州北部的森林中，是一片被封存的钢铁和泥土的休耕地，对于其所有者来说，运营成本太高，因为中国竞争对手已经向全球市场大量供应用于电动汽车电池和电子产品的蓝色金属。 。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 06:08:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/western-miners-push-higher-metals-prices-ward-off-chinese-rivals-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>雷诺首席执行官呼吁欧洲电动汽车过渡时间表保持灵活性</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/renault-ceo-calls-flexibility-european-ev-transition-timeline-2024-07-22/</link><description>雷诺首席执行官卢卡·德梅奥(Luca De Meo)在周一向商业日报《回声报》发表的评论中对欧洲向电动汽车转型的时间表表示怀疑，并补充说，如果该汽车制造商想要实现其电动汽车目标，就必须降低成本。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 05:33:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/renault-ceo-calls-flexibility-european-ev-transition-timeline-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：拜登退出后华尔街情绪谨慎</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-22/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 04:41:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>独家：英伟达正在为中国市场准备新版旗舰人工智能芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-preparing-version-new-flaghip-ai-chip-chinese-market-sources-say-2024-07-22/</link><description>三位知情人士称，英伟达正在为中国市场开发一款新的旗舰人工智能芯片，该芯片将与美国当前的出口管制兼容。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 04:02:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-preparing-version-new-flaghip-ai-chip-chinese-market-sources-say-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国菲律宾大使馆要求回应针对新冠疫苗的宣传</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/chinas-philippines-embassy-demands-answers-propaganda-against-covid-vaccine-2024-07-22/</link><description>中国驻菲律宾大使馆周一表示，美国应尽快就其针对中国COVID-19疫苗的虚假宣传向菲律宾人民作出解释。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 02:37:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/chinas-philippines-embassy-demands-answers-propaganda-against-covid-vaccine-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>渣打银行关联的中国渤海银行寻求处置 40 亿美元不良贷款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/stanchart-linked-china-bohai-seeks-dispose-4-bln-bad-loans-2024-07-22/</link><description>中国渤海银行周一表示，由于中国经济步履蹒跚和房地产行业问题日益严重，迫使银行处置不良资产，该银行正计划出售价值290亿元人民币（合39.9亿美元）的不良贷款。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 02:33:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/stanchart-linked-china-bohai-seeks-dispose-4-bln-bad-loans-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国下调短期和长期利率</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cuts-short-long-term-rates-2024-07-22/</link><description>中国周一将短期和长期利率下调 10 个基点，央行表示旨在支持经济增长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 02:17:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cuts-short-long-term-rates-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>台湾开始年度军事演习 旨在紧密模拟实战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-starts-annual-war-games-aiming-closely-mimic-actual-combat-2024-07-22/</link><description>周一，在一年一度的汉光战争游戏开始之际，台湾在一条战略河流上进行了反登陆演习，今年的目标是尽可能接近实战，没有剧本，模拟如何击退中国的进攻。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 02:17:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-starts-annual-war-games-aiming-closely-mimic-actual-combat-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>失火油轮被海岸警卫队扣留后进入马来西亚码头区</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/fire-hit-oil-tanker-enters-malaysia-fpso-bertam-terminal-area-data-shows-2024-07-22/</link><description>伦敦证券交易所集团 (LSEG) 和 Kpler 的航运数据显示，一艘上周在新加坡附近发生碰撞的油轮在周日被地方当局拦截后，于周一早上进入马来西亚 Bertam 浮动油码头区域。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 01:36:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/fire-hit-oil-tanker-enters-malaysia-fpso-bertam-terminal-area-data-shows-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>小鹏汽车与大众成立项目公司推出新的电动汽车架构</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-volkswagen-set-up-project-house-roll-out-new-ev-architecture-2024-07-22/</link><description>中国电动汽车（EV）制造商小鹏汽车周一表示，已与德国汽车制造商大众汽车公司合作建立了工程师项目室，以加快新电动汽车架构的开发进程。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 01:03:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-volkswagen-set-up-project-house-roll-out-new-ev-architecture-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>拜登结束连任竞选，美元走软，兑日元下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-eases-biden-ends-reelection-bid-yuan-steady-after-rate-cut-2024-07-22/</link><description>美元兑一篮子货币周一小幅回落，而兑日元大幅下跌，因投资者关注美国总统乔·拜登结束连任竞选的决定以及美联储和日本央行的下一步举措。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 00:48:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-eases-biden-ends-reelection-bid-yuan-steady-after-rate-cut-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>部长表示，菲律宾正在考虑与法国、加拿大和新西兰签署防务协定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-eyes-defence-pacts-with-france-canada-nz-minister-says-2024-07-22/</link><description>菲律宾国防部长周一表示，菲律宾正在寻求与加拿大、法国、新西兰和其他国家达成互惠的部队准入协议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 00:43:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-eyes-defence-pacts-with-france-canada-nz-minister-says-2024-07-22/</guid></item></channel></rss>